1. **User Registration** - Complete flow from sign-up through wallet creation
2. **Post Item for Sale** - Item creation with IPFS storage, Ethereum contract interaction, and Firestore/Elasticsearch synchronization
3. **Search Items** - Elasticsearch-powered search functionality
4. **Purchase Item** - End-to-end purchase flow with Libra payment and smart contract updates
5. **Mark Item as Delivered** - Delivery confirmation with payment release and item removal from search index
6. **Leave Review** - Review submission to both Ethereum and Firestore
